1902
02:23:31,000 --> 02:23:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda njegovi postupci kaže, on volio možda popit ili poest nešto.

1903
02:23:36,000 --> 02:23:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, ako to sablažnjava brata ranjive savijesti,

1904
02:23:39,000 --> 02:23:42,000
