1909
02:23:58,000 --> 02:24:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ono, stvarno jedan velikan koji...

1910
02:24:01,000 --> 02:24:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] U njemu sam baš vidio taj Pavlovski sličan neumorni evangelizacijski žark

1911
02:24:05,000 --> 02:24:09,000
